I '''Unibetsedåt Guåhan''' (pat ''University of Guam'' gi Engles ya matungo' lokkue' komu ''U.O.G.'') un kuatro años na ''land-grant institution'' giya sengsong [[Mangilao]] gi islan Guåhan gi [[tasen Pasifiku]]. Ma'''accredit'' ni [[Western Association of Schools and Colleges]] ya ha ofrefresi 35 na degree programs gi Pregrådu yan 13 gi Maestru.

Gi populasion i unibetsedåt, 90% mantaotao Asianu yan Islas Pasifiku, ya kasi 70% man''full-time''. 

== Historia ==

I Unibetsedåt Guåhan ma'establisa finene'na gi 1952 komu ''two-year teacher training school'', mas matungo' komu ''Territorial College of Guam''. Gi 1960, ma'establisa i kolehio gi prisente na lokasion gi talo' na distritu Mangilao. Gi 1965, ma'''accredit'' i kolehio komu ''four-year, degree granting institution''. Matto 1968, kumahulo' i mineggai estudiante gi 1,800 ya i empleao i unibetsedåt kumahulo' asta 130. Mapo'lu na ''land grant institution'' ni [[Kongreson Estados Unidos]] gi 1972.

== Eskuela siha ==

I Unibetsedåt Guåhan ha ofrefresi 35 na ''bachelor's degrees'' yan 13 na ''master's degrees''. 

